[49m[38;5;10m+    195[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    196[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    197[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A clinical-trial recruitment conversationalist decomposes into ten logical stages: trial-and-content-corpus governance, candidate-cohort identification with HIPAA-preparatory-research compliance, channel entry with trial-context establishment, input safety and identity-context loading, IRB-approved trial-description delivery, structured pre-screen administration with deterministic scoring, output safety with coercion-and-benefit-promise detection, pre-screen disposition with warm coordinator handoff and CTMS integration, do-not-contact-discipline operationalization, and audit logging with research-recordkeeping retention. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.9 carry forward; this recipe adds five new ones (per-trial IRB-approved-content corpus governance as architectural primitive, per-trial pre-screen-instrument formalization with deterministic scoring, coercion and benefit-promise detection as output-safety primitive, coordinator-handoff infrastructure with per-trial routing, and research-context PHI handling with separately-governed storage where required).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    198[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    199[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    200[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── TRIAL + CONTENT CORPUS GOVERNANCE ─────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    201[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    202[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Trial onboarding]                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    203[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-trial IRB-approved recruitment plan              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-trial inclusion and exclusion criteria           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    205[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-trial study-description content (overview, FAQ,  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      visit schedule, compensation, risks, regulatory)     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-trial pre-screen instrument with criterion-by-   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      criterion scoring rules                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-trial language-and-reading-level variants        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-trial coordinator-routing configuration          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-trial CTMS integration mapping                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-trial special-population protocols where         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      applicable                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-trial do-not-contact policy                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Per-trial content lifecycle]                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - IRB approval date and version                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Effective date and expiration date                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Amendment workflow (protocol amendment triggers      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      content re-review and re-approval)                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Annual continuing-review touchpoint                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Multi-trial registry]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Trial identifier, title, status, sponsor type        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Site list with per-site IRB approval                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Funding source and regulatory framework              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active recruitment window                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: trial registry; per-trial content packages;    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    per-trial pre-screen instruments; per-trial routing    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    configurations]                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── CANDIDATE COHORT IDENTIFICATION ───────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Cohort identification (HIPAA preparatory-research)]    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - EHR-data-warehouse query against trial inclusion     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      and exclusion criteria the chart can evaluate        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Query results filtered for active patients with      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      reachable contact information                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - HIPAA-preparatory-research provisions enforced       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - IRB-approved query and outreach plan                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Outreach channel selection per IRB-approved plan]      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recruitment letter (postal mail) with QR code        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - SMS recruitment notification (with TCPA compliance)  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-portal recruitment notification              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-channel IRB approval                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-channel TCPA, HIPAA, and contact-preference      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      compliance                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Self-identified-candidate channels]                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Institutional study-finder website                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Referral from partner physician                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recruitment-vendor channel                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Direct trial-link entry                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Candidate identifier resolution]                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - For institution-identified candidates: candidate is  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      an existing patient with known identifier            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - For self-identified candidates: candidate-provided   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      data; identity verification deferred to coordinator  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      handoff or screening visit per IRB-approved plan     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: candidate outreach record with consent-to-be-  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    contacted disposition; do-not-contact records          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    initialized for declines]                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
