[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    276[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Per-trial entry surfaces]                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    277[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recruitment-letter QR code (deep link with trial     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    278[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      identifier)                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - SMS recruitment link                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    280[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-portal recruitment notification              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    281[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Institutional study-finder navigation                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    282[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Direct trial-page chat embed                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Trial-context establishment]                           │
