[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Load per-trial content package                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Load per-trial pre-screen instrument                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Load per-trial coordinator-routing configuration     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Load per-trial special-population protocols where    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      applicable                                           │
