[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    317[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    318[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Standard input safety primitives from recipe 11.1]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    319[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prompt-injection detection                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    320[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - PHI minimization                                     │
