[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    324[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Trial-context-aware input handling]                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    325[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Inputs are interpreted in the active trial's         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    326[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      context                                              │
