[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    330[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Identity context loading where authenticated]          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    331[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Existing patient: load minimal preparatory-research  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    332[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      profile from EHR (problem-list summary,              │
