[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    380[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── STRUCTURED PRE-SCREEN ADMINISTRATION ──────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    381[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    382[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Pre-screen consent]                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    383[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot asks candidate's consent to begin pre-screen     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    384[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot frames pre-screen as not-yet-enrollment          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    385[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot frames data use per IRB-approved plan            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    386[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Candidate consents or declines                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    387[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    388[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Per-criterion question administration]                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    389[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot asks each pre-screen question in IRB-approved    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    390[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      language at candidate's reading level and language   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    391[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot captures candidate response                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    392[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot scores response deterministically against        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    393[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      criterion (pass, fail, uncertain)                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    394[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot does not freestyle questions                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    395[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot does not infer eligibility from off-instrument   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    396[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      disclosures                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    397[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    398[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Branching logic]                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    399[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Some criteria are evaluated only conditional on      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    400[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      others (e.g., pregnancy criterion only for women of  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    401[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      childbearing potential)                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    402[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Branching is IRB-approved and deterministic          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    403[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    404[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Special-population protocol enforcement where          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    405[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   applicable]                                              │
