[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    530[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Research-context PHI handling]                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    531[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recruitment-conversation PHI tagged as research      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    532[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      context                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    533[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Storage in separately-keyed enclave where            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    534[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      institutional policy or trial-specific IRB plan      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    535[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      requires                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    536[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Retention sized to longest of: HIPAA's six-year      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    537[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      minimum, FDA recordkeeping requirements (typically   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    538[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      two years post-FDA-approval or two years after       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    539[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      investigation discontinuation, whichever is later    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    540[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      under 21 CFR), Common Rule recordkeeping (typically  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    541[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      three years after research completion), state-       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    542[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      specific provisions, sponsor-specific provisions,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    543[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      institutional policy                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    544[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    545[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Operational telemetry per trial]                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    546[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Engagement rate (candidate engages with bot after    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    547[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      outreach)                                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    548[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Trial-description-completion rate                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    549[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pre-screen-completion rate                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    550[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pass-rate per criterion                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    551[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Coordinator-handoff completion rate                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    552[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Screening-visit-show rate (downstream metric)        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    553[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Screening-visit-eligibility rate (downstream metric) │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    554[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Enrollment rate (downstream metric)                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    555[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Coordinator-time-per-enrollment improvement          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    556[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-cohort metric slices (language, channel,         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    557[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      reading level, demographic)                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    558[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    559[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Sampled clinical-and-regulatory review]                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    560[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Random sample plus targeted sample of pre-screen     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    561[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      conversations, fail-on-criterion conversations, and  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    562[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coordinator-handoffs                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    563[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Reviewers (research-quality leadership) tag failure  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    564[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      modes (off-script, coercion-violation, benefit-      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    565[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      promise-violation, scope-violation, citation-gap,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    566[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      tone-failure, mandatory-reporting-handling-          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    567[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      failure)                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    568[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - IRB-approved-content-corpus revisions driven by      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    569[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      review findings with IRB re-approval                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    570[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
