[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    572[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: audit trail; research-recordkeeping            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    573[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    artifacts; telemetry; learning signals; IRB-content    │
